item.title: Garden of Eatin': Carrots with Jon Glover & Marisa Pinson
item.description: Jon Glover (@gloveboxx) and Marisa Pinson (@marisapinson) of On Brand join the 'boys to talk the Hollywood Arby's, line cutting, and the history behind "Animal Style" before talking all things carrots in the final episode of The Garden of Eatin': Veggie Table: The Green Gobblin'. Plus another edition of Drank or Stank. Watch this episode at youtube.com/doughboysmedia Get ad-free episodes at patreon.com/doughboys Get Doughboys merch at kinshipgoods... Feed: https://rss.art19.com/doughboys

item.title: The Cars and Adventures of Monterey Car Week 2024
item.description: Matt Farah and Zack Klapman cover some ground! They talk about the incredible hypercars and restomods of Monterey Car Week 2024; how to do that week as cheaply as possible; crazy things seen in traffic; a comparison of the McLaren Artura and the McLaren 750S; a hint to the car Matt bought; how often you can replace carpet; the Evoluto Ferrari; Tuthill GT ONE concept; and answer a variety of Patreon questions... Feed: https://feeds.simplecast.com/c2RzTGta
